DOC.brief_summary: The purpose of this study is to determine the safety, tolerability and blood levels of AZD5847 after daily oral dosing for 14 days.
DOC.brief_title: A Study in Healthy Volunteers to Assess Safety and Blood Levels of AZD5847 After Multiple Doses Over 14 Days
DOC.criteria: BMI between 1830 Use of drugs that inhibit or induce cytochrome P450 3A4 enzymes History of presence of gastrointestinal, hepatic or renal disease
